| Canvas section        | Group answer                                                         |
| --------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Game title            | Password Defender                                                    |
| Target audience       | Teenagers and university students                                    |
| Cyber-safety topic    | Password safety                                                      |
| Learning objective    | Players learn to create strong passwords and protect accounts        |
| Game format           | Quiz game / Scenario-based digital game                              |
| Core gameplay loop    | Read challenge → Choose answer → Get feedback → Earn points          |
| UX design choices     | Bright cyber theme, large buttons, icons and clear layout            |
| Accessibility choices | Large text, simple words and high contrast colours                   |
| Reward and motivation | Stars, badges, points and levels                                     |
| Success measure       | Players correctly identify strong passwords and explain safety rules |
